fields.description:
Tamar River Cruises Showcase the magnificent Cataract Gorge and the beautiful Tamar Valley on boat cruises that range from 50 minutes to 2.5 hours. 

You can spend the day relaxing on the boat as you enjoy local cheese and wine, or you can have a small tour of the Cataract Gorge.

fields.name: Evandale Market
fields.description:
Evandale hosts a regular country market every Sunday, from around 8:00am until around 1:30pm. These markets are located in Falls Park, on Logan Road.

There's a great variety of stalls, including fantastic local produce, secondhand books, food vans, general bric-a-brac and local crafts. There's even pony rides for the kids!
fields.address: Logan Road, Evandale, TAS

fields.name: Saturday morning Harvest Market
fields.description:
